---

<section class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-hillcrop-green-dark mb-6">Join Our Dedicated Team</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                HillCrop is a fast-growing company that requires the services of qualified, experienced, self-motivated, and competent personnel to fill various vacancies that exist within the organization. We value and reward competent hands.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-8 border-yellow-500 p-12 rounded-xl shadow-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">No Current Job Openings</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                While we are not currently hiring for any specific roles, we always welcome expressions of interest from highly qualified and motivated professionals in the energy sector.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-md text-gray-700">
                You may send your detailed CV and cover letter for future consideration to: 
                <a href="mailto:team@hillcropenergy.com" class="font-semibold text-hillcrop-green hover:text-blue-700 transition">team@hillcropenergy.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</section>